  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Universal-Piece-Sword-Tier-List-cover.jpg?fit=1200%2C675\" alt=\"A Universal Piece character is holding a metal pipe\" fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\tScreenshot by The Escapist\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\tGotta have the right blade to slash some enemies.\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv id=\"wp-block-gamurs-article-metadata-1033586\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e|\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp id=\"wp-block-gamurs-article-metadata__date-and-time__published__1033586\" data-datetime=\"Jun 5, 2025 06:51 am UTC-4\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPublished: Jun 5, 2025 06:51 am\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003cp data-characters=\"461\" data-injectable=\"true\" data-video=\"true\"\u003eOne thing we love about \u003cem\u003eUniversal Piece\u003c/em\u003e is how the game allows you to progress in a multitude of different ways. Depending on what Fruit you use, you can make the game easier or harder for yourself. The same goes for weapons. If you aren’t big on powerful Fruits, you can always grab a trusty blade and destroy your enemies the old-fashioned way, especially with a good Sword. To help you pick the best blade, we made this \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eUniversal Piece\u003c/em\u003e Sword Tier List\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n    \u003cdiv data-current-count=\"0\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"table-of-contents\"\u003eTable of contents\u003